{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L993","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIControl","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"control","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the specified annotation."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"control","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The control that was tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you specify is a descendant of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view via the "},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method, you can specify the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom accessory views using the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView"},{"text":" protocol’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"leftAccessoryView"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rightAccessoryView"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"text":"Related examples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutView":{"title":"MLNCalloutView","abstract":[{"text":"A protocol for a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"text":" subclass that displays information about a selected","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation near that annotation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNCalloutView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}]}}}